.TH R_SET_FILE_LOCK 3 "24 Dec 2005" "Karma Distribution"
.SH EXPERIMENTAL_FUNC
r_set_file_lock \- Grab or release the lock on a file.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <karma_r.h>
.sp
.B flag r_set_file_lock
.sp
(int fd, flag lock, flag do_wait)
.SH DESCRIPTION
Grab or release the lock on a file.
.IP \fIfd\fP 1i
The file descriptor to (un)lock.
.IP \fIlock\fP 1i
If TRUE, the file is locked, else it is unlocked.
.IP \fIdo_wait\fP 1i
If TRUE, the routine will wait until the lock is grabbed.
.SH RETURN VALUE
TRUE on success, else FALSE.
.SH Multi-threading Level
Unsafe.
